'''溴化钯'''是一种[[钯|钯]]的溴化物，化学式为{{化學式|鈀|溴|2}}，25℃时密度为5.173 g/mL。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chemicalbook.com/ProductChemicalPropertiesCB8853059.htm|title=溴化钯|accessdate=2016-08-22|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2018-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180829110141/http://www.chemicalbook.com/ProductChemicalPropertiesCB8853059.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 它广泛作为商品出售，用作钯化学的起始原料，尽管比[[氯化钯|氯化钯]]少见。与氯化钯类似，溴化钯不溶于水，但加热时能溶于[[乙腈|乙腈]]，并以单聚体形式形成[[加合物|加合物]]：<ref>{{cite journal | title = Palladium complexes based on optically active terpene derivatives of ethylenediamine | journal = Russian Journal of Coordination Chemistry | volume = 34 | issue = 11 | year = 2008 | doi = 10.1134/S1070328408110110 | pages = 855–857 | author = O. A. Zalevskaya, E. G. Vorob’eva1, I. A. Dvornikova and A. V. Kuchin}}</ref>

: PdBr<sub>2</sub> + 2 MeCN → PdBr<sub>2</sub>(MeCN)<sub>2</sub>

== 制备 ==
溴化钯可以由钯和[[氢溴酸|氢溴酸]]反应而成。<ref name="brauer">[[Georg_Brauer|Georg Brauer]] (Hrsg.) u. a.: ''Handbuch der Präparativen Anorganischen Chemie.'' 3., umgearbeitete Auflage. Band III, Ferdinand Enke, Stuttgart 1981, ISBN 3-432-87823-0, S. 1730.</ref>它也可以由其组成元素直接化合而成。<ref name="Catherine E. Housecroft">{{Literatur | Autor = Catherine E. Housecroft | Titel = Inorganic Chemistry | Verlag = Pearson Education | ISBN = 0130399132 | Jahr = 2005 | Online = {{Google Buch | BuchID = _1gFM51qpAMC | Seite = 686 }} | Seiten = 686 }}</ref>

== 性质 ==
溴化钯是一种深棕色的针状晶体。它不溶于水和有机溶剂，但可溶于氢卤酸。<ref name="brauer" />它是[[单斜晶系|单斜晶系]]的，空间群 P2<sub>1</sub>/c (No. 14)，[[晶格参数|晶格参数]] a = 659 pm、b = 396 pm、c = 2522 pm 和β = 92.6°<ref name="Lax" /> 

== 用处==
溴化钯可以用作有机合成的催化剂。<ref name="Jiro Tsuji">{{Literatur | Autor = [[Jiro_Tsuji|Jiro Tsuji]] | Titel = Palladium Reagents and Catalysts: New Perspectives for the 21st Century | Verlag = John Wiley & Sons | ISBN = 0470021195 | Jahr = 2006 | Online = {{Google Buch | BuchID = 4X_oieJRtIUC | Seite = 344 }} | Seiten = 344 }}</ref>

